  <entry>
    <title>Linux 常用命令</title>
    <link href="/2023/09/12/linux-command/"/>
    <url>/2023/09/12/linux-command/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ping"><a href="#ping" class="headerlink" title="ping"></a>ping</h1><p>查看与主机是否连通</p><blockquote><p>ping baidu.com</p></blockquote><h1 id="telnet"><a href="#telnet" class="headerlink" title="telnet"></a>telnet</h1><p>执行telnet指令开启终端机阶段作业，并登入远端主机。</p><blockquote><p>telnet ip port</p></blockquote><h1 id="安装Redis"><a href="#安装Redis" class="headerlink" title="安装Redis"></a>安装Redis</h1><blockquote><p>sudo yum install epel-release</p><p> sudo yum update</p></blockquote><p>安装</p><blockquote><p>sudo yum install redis</p></blockquote><p>启动</p><blockquote><p>sudo systemctl start redis</p></blockquote><p>校验</p><blockquote><p>sudo systemctl status redis<br>redis-cli ping</p></blockquote><p>重启</p><blockquote><p>   sudo systemctl restart redis</p></blockquote><p><strong>配置文件在：&#x2F;etc&#x2F;redis.conf</strong></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
